"product_introduce":"<p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">三百山国家级风景名胜区位于江西省安远县境内东南部。东邻寻乌县，地跨濂江乡、风山乡、镇岗乡、新园乡。是安远县东南边境诸山峰的合称，地处赣、粤、闽三省交界处。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">三百山国家级风景名胜区</span>2002<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月被国务院批准为第四批国家级重点风景名胜区；</span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">2004<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月被中共江西省委宣传部列为第三批全省爱国主义教育基地； </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年被评为江西省十大特色美景之一。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">三百山国家级风景名胜区位于江西省安远县东南部边境。地理坐标为：东经</span>115°14&#39;56&quot;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，北纬</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">25°00&#39;07&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。东邻寻乌县，地跨濂江乡、风山乡、镇岗乡、新园乡。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">属武夷山脉东段北坡余脉交错地带，是长江水系之贡江与珠江水系之东江的分水岭，是东江的源头，三百山国家级风景名胜区气候多为亚热带季风性湿润气候，年平均气温</span>15.1°C<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，最冷月（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月）平均气温低</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5.8°C</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，最热月（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月）平均气温</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">23.3°C</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，无霜期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">260</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天，年平均降雨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1680</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">－</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月为雨季，降雨量占全年的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">53%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，相对湿度大于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">80%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，年日照时数</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1622</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小时。粤港居民饮用水的发源地，也是全国唯一对香港同胞具有饮水思源特殊意义的旅游胜地。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">三百山在</span>80<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年代中期被发现，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1985</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年被安远县人民政府列为县级自然保护区；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1993</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月被国家林业部批准为国家级森林公园；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1995</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月被江西省人民政府列为省级重点风景名胜区；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月被全国保护母亲河工作领导小组命名为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">首批全国保护母亲河行动</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生态教育示范基地；</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">2002<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月被国务院（国函</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">[2002]40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">号）批准为第四批国家级重点风景名胜区；</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2004</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月被中共江西省委宣传部列为第三批全省爱国主义教育基地； </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年被评为江西省十大特色美景之一。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>",
