"product_introduce":"<p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">龙南虔心小镇景区位于龙南县临塘乡东坑村，景区入口位于</span>105<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">国道边，距大广高速公路龙南南出口</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千米，距龙南站</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">26</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">千米，景区总体规划</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">万亩。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">龙南虔心小镇景区以特有的茶叶、土鸡、脐橙、油茶、腐竹等生态农业产业为核心基础，以</span>“<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">虔</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">文化为主题，结合丰富的山水茶竹资源打造的集自然风景、客家民俗、虔茶文化为一体的旅游度假景区。</span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">2018<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，龙南虔心小镇景区被江西省旅发委评为江西省</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级旅游景区。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">龙南虔心小镇景区，生产基地将农业生态和旅游度假相互结合起来，是集多功能于一体的创新复合生态体验区。中国科学院植物研究所设立了虔心小镇研究示范基地，成立了中国科学院农业科学推广站，在旅游度假方面，龙南虔心小镇景区重点打造樱花谷、镜心湖、沐心谷、虔心院四大景区，已完成规划设计。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一期樱花谷、镜心湖核心景区已经建成一座虔茶文化馆，以及手工油坊、腐竹坊、酒坊等系列</span>“<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">虔工坊</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">“<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">竹林宴遇</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">虔心荟</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">特色餐厅及</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">四闲山房</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">竹隐山居</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">村落等餐饮、住宿配套设施已投入使用。其它与自然相融合的休闲度假旅游基础设施正在分步建设中。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>",
