"product_introduce":"<p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">庐陵文化生态园位于江西省吉安市吉州区城北、赣江之滨，整个公园是利用螺子山山体和滞洪区为建设用地打造的一个生态公园，总面积约</span>4000<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">余亩。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">庐陵文化生态园，分为庐陵文化展示区、庐陵湖景观区、生态景观区、综合休闲娱乐区、滨江景观区、商务度假区六大区域。</span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公园于</span>2011<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日建成开园，同年被江西省旅游局评为</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">江西省十大新旅游景区</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年获批为国家</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级景区。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">庐陵文化生态园以丘陵和平原、湿地为主要地形地貌。螺子山为生态园最高点，海拔</span>142.1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米。庐陵湖面积占文化生态园四分之一。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align: justify;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">庐陵文化生态园为亚热带季风湿润性气候，雨量充沛，日照充足，四季分明。年平均气温在</span>15.1—18.1℃<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">之间，年平均降水量</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1,421.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">毫米，年平均无霜期</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">284</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>",
